{"tid":982305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台北市一女童被砍殺　兇徒被移送偵查途中　台灣公眾義憤到場追打","createTime":"2019-01-15T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T08:58:48.000Z","uid":47714,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93d4edd53cf19b24cdbc799fbbc618b9531724dd","tid":982305,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/e/News.aspx?NewsID=133734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D133734&d=a6jwj76mG8mcAc9%2FaZOaesKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=cd5d2bfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D133734&h=ed063d90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/e/News.aspx?NewsID=133734</a><br />\n<br />\n內湖今（28）日發生隨機砍殺女童案件。警方獲報後立即趕往現場逮捕兇嫌，送至西湖派出所進行偵訊。殺童案兇嫌晚間改送至士林地檢署，現場配有大批鎮暴警力全面戒備。兇嫌抵達現場時，慘遭現場民眾圍毆、怒罵，氣氛火爆。<br />\n<br />\n殺童案兇嫌泯滅人性的行為引起全台民眾撻伐，兇嫌下午步出派出所時，遭現場民眾怒罵、推擠，現場氣憤火爆，警方因考慮到安全問題，將嫌犯退回派出所改由偵防車移送。為防止圍毆事件再度發生，晚間兇嫌移送士林地檢署時，檢方已先請大批警力拎著盾牌進駐現場。不過，雖有大批警方持盾牌戒備，仍敵不過民眾滿腔怒火，王嫌抵達現場時，慘遭數十名民眾痛毆、怒罵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160328004270-260401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20160328004270-260401&d=a6jwj76mG8mcAc9%2FaZOaesKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=c9bc56b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160328004270-260401</a><br />\n<br />\n台北市內湖區環山路發生小女童命案，4歲女童遭王姓男子砍殺身首異處。女童當時和母親一起在住家附近騎車，因事出突然，母親來不及搶救，親眼目睹愛女被殺，幾乎崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n殘殺4歲女童的王姓兇嫌下午3時移送內湖分局時，遭到憤怒民眾追打，只好躲回警局。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-03-28/656/20160328004478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-03-28%2F656%2F20160328004478.jpg&h=17f7e1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場聚集憤怒民眾，上前追打王姓嫌犯。（楊兆元攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-03-28/656/20160328005201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-03-28%2F656%2F20160328005201.jpg&h=a0493895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n憤怒民眾追打殺女童兇嫌。（方濬哲攝）"},{"pid":"8f35fde2a3950d6b34b2db7ad1aec0c0163b43bc","tid":982305,"uid":211461,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"警察應該係專登放佢出黎俾市民打一打先再收返入警署"},{"pid":"675e726aa200ef287433b70eec91fcddf41dbecc","tid":982305,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"同鄉之情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1496ae4b643ce7bd8169c9a92f3614f0dc3032","tid":982305,"uid":11962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"回帶？"},{"pid":"bca0c0643c3ef443eefbb93989e43a9e14b8d950","tid":982305,"uid":9736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhbmTDX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhbmTDX.png&h=4a0e1690&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdda95c25a4a263433b35bf90efbd31cf841371b","tid":982305,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"763400ad405140128a29c55a0061639bc751753c","tid":982305,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"回帶"},{"pid":"f02a05c2d6c85f39764af2696895c043a01ec6f5","tid":982305,"uid":196750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdda95c25a4a263433b35bf90efbd31cf841371b","tid":982305,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"錯！法律源自人類公義，如果某國法律包容犯重罪的罪犯，人民就有權行血親復仇！"},{"pid":"774abd40eb83c24e496d38a3abe9af116903cb96","tid":982305,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T0